Class ArtConnectionOnDisk

java.lang.Object
  com.softwareag.wx.is.config.autoSetup.ArtConnectionOnDisk

public class ArtConnectionOnDisk
extends java.lang.Object

Represents an ART adapter connection on the file system. This allows changes even if the package is not loaded.
